# skelm dashboard

This is a local operations dashboard scaffolded by `skelm dashboard init`.

```sh
skelm gateway start --foreground
skelm dashboard start
```

By default the dashboard listens on `127.0.0.1:14740` and proxies to the
gateway at `127.0.0.1:14738`. Port `14739` is left free for the gateway proxy.

Configuration lives in `dashboard.config.mts`. For bearer-auth gateways, set
`SKELM_DASHBOARD_TOKEN` or pass `--token` to `skelm dashboard start`.

The dashboard server proxies `/api/*` to the configured gateway URL, so the
browser never stores the gateway bearer token.
